{
  "stem": "6526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were only, let's say, reigning or seeing that we support the places of worship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We support our main rabbi, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I have a picture of one president of the-- of the Kehillah, of the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when the-- when the war broke out, the Kehillah disintegrated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the mayor of the town received an order from the Germans to organize to get 10 Jews to make a Judenrat, like a Kehillah.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they are to be responsible not to the Jews, but responsible to the Germans, whatever the Germans will have over us to place or to want or to do.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father was one of them to be designated as a member of the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly religious people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were some religious wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some-- and some were even not wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just known because maybe their forefathers or their immediate family was more learned than not learned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was-- not everyone tried to push himself into being in the Kehillah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were very well aware of because going to school, and specialty the school, and the newspapers that we read, the Yiddish papers, because we used to get a Jewish paper.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Warsaw, there was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were various Yiddish papers, and they were writing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we heard what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we very much were very well aware.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the propaganda in Poland in the 1930s, let's say, '37, '38 when Hitler started to take in Austria, and then he took Sudeten, and then he started to ask a corridor through [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's the upper part where [INAUDIBLE], or Danzig.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we realized that they may ask for something like that, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
